              No. Flow is a one-time purchase. You get the full app and one year of updates. After that year, the app keeps working — you just stop receiving new features until you renew. An optional cloud sync subscription is planned for a future phase, but it will never be required.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group py-6">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-brand text-lg font-medium text-navy dark:text-white">
